{"title":"记LeetCode每日一题-单调栈Plus+复习单调栈-C++","uid":"16628ff8472695adf497f3bbda476921","slug":"LeetCode_daily_zhan","date":"2023-12-12T03:30:20.000Z","updated":"2023-12-24T08:29:03.219Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/LeetCode_daily_zhan.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121132507.webp","content":"<h1 id=\"单调栈\"><a href=\"#单调栈\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"单调栈\"></a>单调栈</h1><blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>求下个更大的元素  &#x2F; 下下个</li>\n<li>求单调的前缀和、后缀和</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"2454-下一个更大的元素IV\"><a href=\"#2454-下一个更大的元素IV\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2454.下一个更大的元素IV\"></a><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/next-greater-element-iv/description/\">2454.下一个更大的元素IV</a></h1><blockquote>\n<p>给你一个下标从 <strong>0</strong> 开始的非负整数数组 <code>nums</code> 。对于 <code>nums</code> 中每一个整数，你必须找到对应元素的 <strong>第二大</strong> 整数。</p>\n<p>如果 <code>nums[j]</code> 满足以下条件，那么我们称它为 <code>nums[i]</code> 的 <strong>第二大</strong> 整数：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>j &gt; i</code></li>\n<li><code>nums[j] &gt; nums[i]</code></li>\n<li>恰好存在 <strong>一个</strong> <code>k</code> 满足 <code>i &lt; k &lt; j</code> 且 <code>nums[k] &gt; nums[i]</code> 。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果不存在 <code>nums[j]</code> ，那么第二大整数为 <code>-1</code> 。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>比方说，数组 <code>[1, 2, 4, 3]</code> 中，<code>1</code> 的第二大整数是 <code>4</code> ，<code>2</code> 的第二大整数是 <code>3</code> ，<code>3</code> 和 <code>4</code> 的第二大整数是 <code>-1</code> 。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>请你返回一个整数数组 <code>answer</code> ，其中 <code>answer[i]</code>是 <code>nums[i]</code> 的第二大整数。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>说人话：就是找到比当前元素第二大的元素</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">输入：nums = [2,4,0,9,6]</span><br><span class=\"line\">输出：[9,6,6,-1,-1]</span><br><span class=\"line\">解释：</span><br><span class=\"line\">下标为 0 处：2 的右边，4 是大于 2 的第一个整数，9 是第二个大于 2 的整数。</span><br><span class=\"line\">下标为 1 处：4 的右边，9 是大于 4 的第一个整数，6 是第二个大于 4 的整数。</span><br><span class=\"line\">下标为 2 处：0 的右边，9 是大于 0 的第一个整数，6 是第二个大于 0 的整数。</span><br><span class=\"line\">下标为 3 处：右边不存在大于 9 的整数，所以第二大整数为 -1 。</span><br><span class=\"line\">下标为 4 处：右边不存在大于 6 的整数，所以第二大整数为 -1 。</span><br><span class=\"line\">所以我们返回 [9,6,6,-1,-1] 。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"解题记录\"><a href=\"#解题记录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解题记录\"></a>解题记录</h2><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121247398.png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><ol>\n<li><p>先放一个单调栈的模版</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> stack[<span class=\"number\">100001</span>];    <span class=\"comment\">//模拟栈</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> cur = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;        <span class=\"comment\">//栈内元素</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> result[<span class=\"number\">100001</span>][<span class=\"number\">2</span>];   <span class=\"comment\">//保存下标</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">nextGreater</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt;&amp; nums)</span> </span>&#123;   </span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//遍历阶段</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>; i&lt;nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>(); i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(cur &gt; <span class=\"number\">0</span> &amp;&amp; nums[stack[cur<span class=\"number\">-1</span>]] &lt; nums[i])&#123;  <span class=\"comment\">//当前的更大，把里面的顶出来</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">// stack[cur-1]      index      i</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"type\">int</span> index = stack[--cur];           <span class=\"comment\">//取出栈顶下标</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                result[index][<span class=\"number\">1</span>] = i;           \t<span class=\"comment\">//下一个更大的下标</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                result[index][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] = cur &gt; <span class=\"number\">0</span> ? stack[cur<span class=\"number\">-1</span>] : <span class=\"number\">-1</span>;     <span class=\"comment\">//上一个更大的下标</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            stack[cur++] = i;   \t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//栈入元素</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//清算阶段</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(cur &gt; <span class=\"number\">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"type\">int</span> index = stack[--cur];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            result[index][<span class=\"number\">1</span>] = <span class=\"number\">-1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            result[index][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] = cur &gt; <span class=\"number\">0</span> ? stack[cur<span class=\"number\">-1</span>] : <span class=\"number\">-1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>关键在于第二次入栈也要保持大 -&gt; 小，如果第一个栈出一个元素，直接加入第二个栈，那样单调性就相反了</p>\n<p>先确定第一个栈要出哪些元素，再去从下向上加入到第二个栈，即可满足单调性</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> stack[<span class=\"number\">100001</span>];    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> cur = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;        </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> stack2[<span class=\"number\">100001</span>];     <span class=\"comment\">//第二次单调栈，都是存下标</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> cur2 = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\">vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt; <span class=\"title\">secondGreaterElement</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt;&amp; nums)</span> </span>&#123;   </span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\">vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt; <span class=\"title\">ans</span><span class=\"params\">(nums.size(), <span class=\"number\">-1</span>)</span></span>;\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//初始为-1，这样就没了结算阶段</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>; i&lt;nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>(); i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(cur2 &gt; <span class=\"number\">0</span> &amp;&amp; nums[stack2[cur2<span class=\"number\">-1</span>]] &lt; nums[i])&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"type\">int</span> index2 = stack2[--cur2];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                ans[index2] = nums[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"type\">int</span> index = cur<span class=\"number\">-1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(cur &gt; <span class=\"number\">0</span> &amp;&amp; nums[stack[cur<span class=\"number\">-1</span>]] &lt; nums[i])&#123;    </span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">//关键在于，第一次栈是小元素，在上面，第二次入栈怎么也保证小元素在上面</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                cur--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> k=cur; k&lt;=index; k++)&#123;      <span class=\"comment\">//这样从底向上移动到第二个栈，就可以保证了</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                stack2[cur2++] = stack[k];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            stack[cur++] = i; </span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"2866-美丽塔II\"><a href=\"#2866-美丽塔II\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2866.美丽塔II\"></a><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/beautiful-towers-ii/description/\">2866.美丽塔II</a></h1><p>12.21每日一题</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>给你一个长度为 <code>n</code> 下标从 <strong>0</strong> 开始的整数数组 <code>maxHeights</code> 。</p>\n<p>你的任务是在坐标轴上建 <code>n</code> 座塔。第 <code>i</code> 座塔的下标为 <code>i</code> ，高度为 <code>heights[i]</code> 。</p>\n<p>如果以下条件满足，我们称这些塔是 <strong>美丽</strong> 的：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code>1 &lt;= heights[i] &lt;= maxHeights[i]</code></li>\n<li><code>heights</code> 是一个 <strong>山脉</strong> 数组。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>如果存在下标 <code>i</code> 满足以下条件，那么我们称数组 <code>heights</code> 是一个 <strong>山脉</strong> 数组：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>对于所有 <code>0 &lt; j &lt;= i</code> ，都有 <code>heights[j - 1] &lt;= heights[j]</code></li>\n<li>对于所有 <code>i &lt;= k &lt; n - 1</code> ，都有 <code>heights[k + 1] &lt;= heights[k]</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>请你返回满足 <strong>美丽塔</strong> 要求的方案中，<strong>高度和的最大值</strong> 。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">输入：maxHeights = [5,3,4,1,1]</span><br><span class=\"line\">输出：13</span><br><span class=\"line\">解释：和最大的美丽塔方案为 heights = [5,3,3,1,1] ，这是一个美丽塔方案，因为：</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 1 &lt;= heights[i] &lt;= maxHeights[i]  </span><br><span class=\"line\">- heights 是个山脉数组，峰值在 i = 0 处。</span><br><span class=\"line\">13 是所有美丽塔方案中的最大高度和。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">输入：maxHeights = [6,5,3,9,2,7]</span><br><span class=\"line\">输出：22</span><br><span class=\"line\">解释： 和最大的美丽塔方案为 heights = [3,3,3,9,2,2] ，这是一个美丽塔方案，因为：</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 1 &lt;= heights[i] &lt;= maxHeights[i]</span><br><span class=\"line\">- heights 是个山脉数组，峰值在 i = 3 处。</span><br><span class=\"line\">22 是所有美丽塔方案中的最大高度和。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"感受\"><a href=\"#感受\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"感受\"></a>感受</h2><p>用单调栈还能去求单调递增或者单调递减的前缀和</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> stack[<span class=\"number\">100005</span>];  <span class=\"comment\">//下标</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> cur = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"title\">maximumSumOfHeights</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt;&amp; nums)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//左侧满足非递减，右侧满足非递增</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//因此可用两次单调栈 O(n) 求出前缀和和后缀和</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> n = nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\">vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span>&gt; <span class=\"title\">af_sum</span><span class=\"params\">(n+<span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"number\">0</span>)</span></span>;   <span class=\"comment\">//包含i的后缀和</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\">vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span>&gt; <span class=\"title\">be_sum</span><span class=\"params\">(n+<span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"number\">0</span>)</span></span>;   <span class=\"comment\">//包含i的前缀和</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//后缀和</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> sum = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> i=n<span class=\"number\">-1</span>; i&gt;=<span class=\"number\">0</span>; i--)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(cur &gt; <span class=\"number\">0</span> &amp;&amp; nums[stack[cur<span class=\"number\">-1</span>]] &gt; nums[i])&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">//cur的大小就是栈里面的元素个数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">//当前元素更小，一个一个清空栈，直到遇到比当前还小的</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                cur--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(cur == <span class=\"number\">0</span>)&#123;       <span class=\"comment\">//栈全被清空了，那么i~n-1 必然全是nums[i]</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                sum = (<span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span>)nums[i]*(n-i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;               <span class=\"comment\">//栈有剩余，i到 栈顶下标 都被清了， 所以后缀和从当前栈顶下标那里转移过来 + 清空个数*nums[i]</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                sum = be_sum[stack[cur<span class=\"number\">-1</span>]]+(<span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span>)(stack[cur<span class=\"number\">-1</span>]-i)*nums[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            be_sum[i] = sum;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            stack[cur++] = i;   </span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//前缀和</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        sum = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;    <span class=\"comment\">//清空之前的记录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        cur = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span> ans = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>; i&lt;n; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">//cur的大小就是栈里面的元素个数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(cur &gt; <span class=\"number\">0</span> &amp;&amp; nums[stack[cur<span class=\"number\">-1</span>]] &gt; nums[i])&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                cur--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(cur == <span class=\"number\">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                sum = (<span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span>)nums[i]*(i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                sum = af_sum[stack[cur<span class=\"number\">-1</span>]]+(<span class=\"type\">long</span> <span class=\"type\">long</span>)(i-stack[cur<span class=\"number\">-1</span>])*nums[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            af_sum[i] = sum;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            stack[cur++] = i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            ans = <span class=\"built_in\">max</span>(ans, <span class=\"number\">0ll</span>+af_sum[i]+be_sum[i]-nums[i]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","text":"还不错的，单调栈Plus+复习单调栈-C++...","permalink":"/post/LeetCode_daily_zhan","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"5.2k","symbolsTime":"5 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"LeetCode","slug":"LeetCode","count":10,"path":"api/categories/LeetCode.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"LeetCode","slug":"LeetCode","count":10,"path":"api/tags/LeetCode.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8D%95%E8%B0%